Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuzzy Legs? Do you think you\Ncould secure those windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll alert me\Nif anything scary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,comes close to\Nthe cottage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When something scary comes\Nclose to the cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me my\Nhiding place is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, you've filled\Nit with everything I need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to survive this awful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I don't have to\Nstep a hoof outside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,until this whole\Nthing is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! You don't\Nhave any carrots?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.33,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have any other fresh\Nveggies you may enjoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe some hay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means I'll\Nneed to go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...ON NIGHTMARE NIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have spooky muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
