Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Give me something{\i0}\N{\i1} sweet to bite! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Nightmare Night,{\i0}\N{\i1} what a fright, ♪{\i0}
