Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nout and about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Nightmare Night, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't suppose\NI could borrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a few pieces of\Nhay from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to stock\Nup on food for Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and you do seem to\Nhave quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We need it for the Apple\NFamily Haunted Maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The scariest maze\Nthat there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what\Nlurks inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sure I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a mummified pony\Nthat just leaped out at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's that crunching\Nsound beneath your hooves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the bones of ponies\Nthat didn't make it out alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,B-b-b-bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those peeled grapes or\Na thousand slimy eyeballs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,starin' at you from\Nbeyond the grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me\Nthey're grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll never\Ntell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what got\Nstuck in her craw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's scary now.\NJust wait until it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's OK. I'll take\Nyour word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!\NIt's Nightmare Night
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're here and not\Nholed up in your cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean what\NI think it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That I foolishly forgot to\Nstock up on food for Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and had to go out\Nto get him something
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but got spooked in\Ntown so I came here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hoping Twilight had some\Nlettuce I could give him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I thought\Nmaybe you'd decided
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to come out with us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, no! I couldn't be\Nout tonight. I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically speaking, you\Nalready are out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I guess that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if you stayed out a\Nlittle longer with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know they'd be super excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You would make them SO\Nhappy if you joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't\Nbelieve their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fluttershy,\Nwhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it\Ngot very, very quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly they\Nrealized
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the BALLOONS HAD\NNEVER BEEN INFLATED!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you about the\Nnight the mannequin came to life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and haunted all the costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A mannequin came to life and\Nhaunted all the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.19,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? What are you\Ndoing here? Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine. In\Nfact, it's more than fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to join you in your\NNightmare Night festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You?\NOut? Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Every Nightmare Night I\Nshut myself in my cottage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and refuse to come\Nout until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just like when\NI was afraid to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't given it a try,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would've found\Nout how much I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'd have missed out\Non how great you sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy with us\Non Nightmare Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that's positively\Nthe most wonderful news
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get dressed up\Nin a costume with us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and play Nightmare\NNight games with us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat candy apples with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Goin' through my\Nfamily's corn maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. The maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if you're up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am! I am ready to\Ntake on Nightmare Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy? No. Headless Pony?\NNo. Vampire Fruit Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, definitely no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Fluttershy, the\Nbeauty of Nightmare Night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you don't have to\Ndress up as something scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This one will look\Ngorgeous on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Period costumes are\Nall the rage this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we encounter\Nsomething terrifying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and need to get\Naway quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All those layers could slow me\Ndown, or worse, make me trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I never\Nconsidered that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never Fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, now this is a real\Nstunner! I call it "Masquerade!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a simple black\Ndress underneath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but with this ornately\Ndecorated mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They can just be so\Ndifficult to see out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but this one has eyeholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What about being able to\Nsee what's to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or right of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose your vision\Nwould be somewhat obscured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first Nightmare\NNight out and about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and we do want you\Nto be comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I just\Nwear the dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sure, dear.\NThat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so plain,\Nit's frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, look at all of you!\NMy costumes fit you to a T!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-ee we're gonna\Nhave the best time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fluttershy,\Nwhere's your costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! You're a robber\Nescaping into the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a NINJA escaping\Ninto the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE BLACK LICORICE\Nescaping into the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Close. I'm going to a masquerade\Nball. Without the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's great!\NIsn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\NGreat costume.\NSo creative!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd save the really\Nscary games for next year
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when Fluttershy's\Nmore used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Round and round and round you\Ngo where you stop nopony knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck beating\NTHAT, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um. It's just\Nthat if I'm blindfolded
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and somepony were to\Nleap out in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never have the\Nchance to defend myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do\Nanything you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just glad\Nyou're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to\Nfinish that game;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another one I KNOW you'll\Nlove! Bobbing for apples!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that, um,\Nwhat happens if,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,when my head is deep\Ndown in the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of scary\Nmonster appears?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I even hear to\Nknow I was under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I made candy bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Each bag has been made\Nwith each of YOU in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,complete with each of\Nyour favorite candies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Take it. Take it!\NWhat are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what if when I'm eating one\Nof these chewy taffies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,my mouth becomes glued shut and\NI can't scream for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness. We've only\Njust started to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Night together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm already taking all\Nthe fun out of it, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not taking\Nout ALL the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like, 90 per--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,--some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's just so many things\Nthat terrify me about tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly predict\Nwhat might upset me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless... YOU were the\None doing the scaring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,HER scaring US?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing you hate\Nis being scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but if YOU'RE the one\Ndoing the scaring then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,....then I can help\Nyou all have fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can still be a\Npart of Nightmare Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you like that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to\Nget ahead of myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I have the PERFECT\Nidea for how I'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet me at my\Ncottage in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited to see\Neverypony soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome{\i0}\N{\i1} to Fluttershy's tea party!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just\Nsay tea party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it's\Na scary tea party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have a seat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Don't be scared of{\i0}\N{\i1} what awaits you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Go on. Pass the sugar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no! There is none!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a terrible host!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Rarity, put your coat on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You need to cover up because no{\i0}\N{\i1}one has complimented your dress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pinkie Pie, look to your left{\i0}\N{\i1}and ask your best friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to pass the cucumber sandwiches!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't!\NThere's nopony there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} That's right. Because she{\i0}\N{\i1} didn't care to show up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} A friend who didn't{\i0}\N{\i1} come through!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must scare you to the core!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Quick, everypony,{\i0}\N{\i1} look behind you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} They're unplanned guests!{\i0}\N{\i1} Your worst nightmare!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} You don't have{\i0}\N{\i1} enough food for them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Oh, no! There's a tiny{\i0}\N{\i1} kitten that needs a home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But you are{\i0}\N{\i1} over-scheduled right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} You don't have time to help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I said, you don't{\i0}\N{\i1} have time to help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This should appear to scare you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you look terrified?\NYou showed up to a party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and everypony was extremely\Ndisappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you imagine\Nanything more upsetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a really\Ngood try, darling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the scares at\NNightmare Night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are of an entirely\Ndifferent nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really\Ncreative, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have\Nthought of... all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just not cut out for\Nthis. Just go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we\Ncouldn't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to. This is the night\Nyou look forward to all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We could...stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. I really want\Nyou all to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how I spend\Nevery Nightmare Night!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny; I actually\Nthought she had an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for something really\Nscary for a second there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She definitely\Ntried her hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I did try my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could have gone\Nwith something a bit scarier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I've\Nbeen taking baby steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's time\Nfor grown up ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose you have any\Nideas how I could do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony's lining up for the\Ncorn maze, y'all. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I can't believe\Nwe're finally doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing\NFluttershy isn't here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because she would NEVER\Nbe able to handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,AGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo...yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What. Is. That. Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like...bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a bunch of dried\Nsticks painted white to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, TRY to keep up the\Nillusion, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, course I do.\NIt was uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy had a point with\Nthe layers on the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,AGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Is it a\Ntunnel? Where does it lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way are we\Nsupposed to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! I don't\Nknow what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Didn't\Nyou help plan this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's\NGranny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I was EVER\Nscared. Cause I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pretty good\Nactress when I wanna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, didn't you\Nknow about any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I gotts admit I\Ndidn't know about any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe they're just tryin' to\Nmake it interestin' for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Granny Smith or\NBig Mac is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those\Npeeled grapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or eyeballs starin' at you from\Nbeyond the grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what WE were\Nsupposed to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why\Nwe're down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really\Nscarin' me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that get down here??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like glue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,AGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so, so sorry,\Ncan you ever forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,FLUTTERSHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you the\Nwhole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That. Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,THE BEST THING EVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was way more terrifying\Nthan the most terrifying thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have thought of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You out-nightmared the scariest\Npart of the corn maze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After you left, I realized\Nthat I wasn't ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to give up on Nightmare Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I asked Granny Smith if I\Ncould try to make the maze
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,even scarier for\Nmy friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You came up with\Nall of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel was the scary figure\Nthat kept scurrying after you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuzzy Legs made the sticky wall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that made it difficult\Nfor you to see and move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course Hairy was the\Nespecially scary monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That was inspired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do\Nthis EVERY YEAR!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We could celebrate Nightmare\NNight together every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is I\Nreally don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You DON'T?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found a way we can all\Nhave a fabulous time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I've also\Nrealized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You all may love\NNightmare Night
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I may be good at being a\Npart of it, but it's no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to see my friends\Nfeel like they're in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I know they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like it. It's\Njust not my cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Just regular tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We do lots of fun\Nthings together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid this just isn't\Ngoing to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm not afraid;\NI'm perfectly fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we are too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I doubted\Nmyself for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now THIS is what I call a\Nperfect Nightmare Night.
